  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eternal Cocoon is a horror adventure game where Olivia, a girl trapped between reality and dreams, must uncover the truth while evading threats and monstrous attacks to choose her own fate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/71d2da51b6896efba2d0dc288de367d7.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/71d2da51b6896efba2d0dc288de367d7.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After encountering a dark shadow, Olivia starts to sense that something is amiss in her life and begins to uncover the secrets of the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/bee737fba357f9a53ea5b4e5379f6efb.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/bee737fba357f9a53ea5b4e5379f6efb.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, she pieces together clues and begins to realize the truth about her life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/34bedc7cb3403bbc7b5912de506afc99.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/34bedc7cb3403bbc7b5912de506afc99.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside the mansion, various traps and dangerous monsters threaten Olivia’s survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/af440a9552fd7052f5b8edc611a8b554.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/af440a9552fd7052f5b8edc611a8b554.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Olivia draws closer to the truth, what fate awaits her?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/6e3e6d1fcf1327314c4852ccaea59005.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/6e3e6d1fcf1327314c4852ccaea59005.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices made at crucial moments and obtaining key items will impact the outcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras/48d304ccf0334738f8d8e348f3e91381.avif?t=1731402581\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860660/extras_big/48d304ccf0334738f8d8e348f3e91381.avif?t=1731402581 width=800 height=462 /></span></p>",
